narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: We learned about the history and tactics of the US Air Forces. We also practiced briefings and presentation techniques.
Understanding of wars the US Air Force has been involved with.

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: This was a very good course overall, perhaps having even more guest lecturers with military experience to help further expose us to the armed services.

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: This is an ROTC specific class so I'm unsure if other students are allowed or would even want to take it.
